  "intent": "Perform magnetic bead-based peptide enrichment on 1-96 samples using a MagDeck module. Add 200\u00b5L MGC binding buffer to each sample well in deep-well plate, incubate 5 minutes, engage magnet for 5 minutes, remove supernatant. Execute two ethanol wash cycles with 400\u00b5L each, removing supernatant between washes. Resuspend pellets in 50\u00b5L MGC elution buffer with manual sonication step, engage magnet for final separation, then transfer 65\u00b5L eluent to 300\u00b5L elution plate.",
